data.description: Charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home situated on a 1.46 acre private lot. Gorgeous hardwood floors throughout main living area. Kitchen offers freshly painted cabinets, new stainless steel updated appliances. Eat in dining area that leads to the back porch. You will love this outdoor entertaining area. Features large deck area, outdoor fire pit, amazing gazebo to relax and entertain friends and family! Everyone will enjoy the above ground pool, featuring a slide and partial deck surround with a large private backyard. Home has a separate formal dining room with a large open concept to the living room. Living room offers a wood burning fireplace. Large master bedroom with plenty of space and tray ceiling . Master bath has new tile floors and separate shower and tub and oversized closet! Split bedroom floor plan with new tile floors in spare bathroom as well. This new listing won't last long! Call today!
